### Welcome to Front Pages.
This page is the produce showcase of our company, using fullpage.js to create it, and gorgeous animation is powered by CSS3. so the best way to walk through this page is using chrome browser.

### Do learn,not pirate.
"open source" is a great spirit of making life better, but I still hope you guys should learn the skill, rather than do the "copy" thing .
